Monique BROWNLEE, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
TOWN SPORTS INTERNATIONAL HOLDINGS, INC. and Majorie Ramos, Defendants-Respondents. 082526
C-987 September Term 2018 Supreme Court of New Jersey. JUNE 13, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000816-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
